[package]
name = "tauri-plugin-context-menu"
version = "0.7.0"
authors = [ "c2r0b",]
description = "Handle native Context Menu in Tauri"
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.59"
exclude = [ "/examples", "/assets", ".DS_Store", "/.github", "/.changes", "/webview-dist", "/webview-src", "package.json", "package-lock.json",]

[dependencies]
lazy_static = "1.4"
time = "0.3.28"

[dependencies.tauri]
version = "1.5"

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
features = [ "derive",]

[target."cfg(target_os = \"windows\")".dependencies]
image = "0.24.7"

[target."cfg(target_os = \"macos\")".dependencies]
cocoa = "0.24.1"
objc = "0.2.7"
libc = "0.2.147"
dispatch = "0.2.0"

[target."cfg(target_os = \"linux\")".dependencies]
gtk = "0.15.1"
gdk = "0.15.1"
glib = "0.15.1"

[target."cfg(target_os = \"windows\")".dependencies.winapi]
version = "0.3"
features = [ "winuser",]

[package]
name = "tauri-plugin-single-instance"
version = "0.0.0"
description = "Ensure a single instance of your tauri app is running."
authors = [ "Tauri Programme within The Commons Conservancy",]
license = "Apache-2.0 OR MIT"
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.64"
exclude = [ "/examples",]

[dependencies]
serde_json = "1"
tauri = "1"
log = "0.4"
thiserror = "1"

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1"
features = [ "derive",]

[target."cfg(target_os = \"linux\")".dependencies]
zbus = "3"

[target."cfg(target_os = \"windows\")".dependencies.windows-sys]
version = "0.52"
features = [ "Win32_System_Threading", "Win32_System_DataExchange", "Win32_Foundation", "Win32_UI_WindowsAndMessaging", "Win32_Security", "Win32_System_LibraryLoader", "Win32_Graphics_Gdi",]

[package]
name = "tauri-plugin-store"
version = "0.0.0"
description = "Simple, persistent key-value store."
authors = [ "Tauri Programme within The Commons Conservancy",]
license = "Apache-2.0 OR MIT"
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.64"

[dependencies]
serde_json = "1"
tauri = "1"
log = "0.4"
thiserror = "1"

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1"
features = [ "derive",]

[package]
name = "tauri-plugin-window-state"
version = "0.1.0"
description = "Save window positions and sizes and restore them when the app is reopened."
authors = [ "Tauri Programme within The Commons Conservancy",]
license = "Apache-2.0 OR MIT"
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.64"

[dependencies]
serde_json = "1"
tauri = "1"
log = "0.4"
thiserror = "1"
bincode = "1.3"
bitflags = "2"

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1"
features = [ "derive",]

[source.vendored-sources]
directory = "cargo/vendor"

[source.crates-io]
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/c2r0b/tauri-plugin-context-menu"]
git = "https://github.com/c2r0b/tauri-plugin-context-menu"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
branch = "main"

[source."https://github.com/tauri-apps/plugins-workspace"]
git = "https://github.com/tauri-apps/plugins-workspace"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
branch = "v1"
